Package: rdmatop
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: real-time TUI monitor for RDMA network interfaces
 rdmatop displays per-queue RDMA counters in a terminal user
 interface, supporting EFA and InfiniBand devices. It refreshes
 counters at a configurable interval and shows rolling averages
 useful for debugging high-performance networking workloads.
